modName: Drachis Argonians and Raptor Feet merged
summary: Combines the textures of Argonian Raptor Feet and Drachis Argonians Mod.
descriptionHtml:
TEXTURES ONLY - Argonian Raptor Feet is required for this. Download here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/19283

Description:
I like both Drachis Argonians mod and Argonian Raptor Feet, I wanted to run both so I decided to combine the textures on my own. Made the male textures compatible with Sundracons male body replacer as well.

Compatibility:
Doesn't work with CBBE body replacer for now. As I'm not much of a texturer, I don't really know how to port the texture to said body replacer. Should probably work with UNP on the other hand.

Credits:
Drachis for DAM textures
mindinavoid for Drachis and Sundracon Compatibility Fix
Artifex0 for ARF mod
